arrival at Red Cross Hospital, the hospital reported.
   There was no immediate claim of responsibility for the attack.
   In the past, members of the Basque separatist organization ETA
have killed policemen and military officers as part of their
violent 20-year campaign for independence of the northern Basque
region.
